### Critical Path Analysis (by inspection of synthesized netlist)

Worst-case path: Register File read → ID Stage decode → EX Stage
  forwarding mux → ALU (32-bit ADD) → EX/MEM register setup
  Estimated: ~8.0 ns (at SS/125°C/1.62V)

Components on critical path:
  RF read mux (32:1):     ~0.4 ns
  ID decode logic:        ~0.5 ns
  Forwarding mux (3:1):   ~0.3 ns
  ALU (32-bit adder):     ~3.5 ns (sky130hd, worst-case)
  EX/MEM pipeline reg:    ~0.3 ns (setup)
  Clock uncertainty:      ~0.4 ns
  ─────────────────────────────────
  Total est. path:        ~5.4 ns (TT corner)
  Worst-case (SS):        ~8.0 ns
  Available period:       20.0 ns
  Est. slack (SS):        ~12.0 ns

